      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i should call them but it's super late and my doctor's office is closed. i just feel like if i take it on an empty stomach when im already low, i'm gonna wake up in a bad way. if i just skip it tonight i'll be fine right? i'll just take a double dose tomorrow morning to make up for it.",
